div1.p: Cicuit Court of the United States, Ninth Judicial Circuit, Western District of Washington Northern Division
In the Matter of Earnest Hutchinson on Habeas Corpus
Writ of Habeas Corpus and Return Thereto
Filed on Return, this day Filed in the U.S. Circuit Court, Western Dist. of Washington. JUL 27 1905. A. Reeves Ayres, Clerk
By A. N. Moore, Deputy Clerk
United States of America, Western District of Washington

I hereby certify and return that I served the annexed Writ of Habeas Corpus on the there-named L.C. Smith, Sheriff of King C. by handing to and leaving a true and correct copy thereof with him at Seattle WA in said District on the 28 day of July, A. D. 1905.
